	   <tr><td colspan=2>But I would guess that Lockpicking could provide the best test of this - use a set of mechanical lockpicks (+2%) and Forthal's gauntlets (sp?) (2%) and try and pick the North Freeport bank door at 193 skill. 193*1.04 = 200.72; 193*1.02 = 196.86 so if they stack, the Rogue should be able to open the door at skill 193; if not (eg if highest modifier works), only at skill 197 (200/1.02=196.07).<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Tue Mar 25 08:05:13 2003</em><br>&nbsp;<br><i><a href=HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=615518 target=_new>Gaell Stormracer, Epic Hierophant of Tunare - &lt;United Kingdoms&gt; Antonius Bayle</a></i></td></tr>
